1%2C%22width%22%3A72%2C%22height%22%3A25%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%22%2C%22x%22%3A87%2C%22y%22%3A600%2C%22width%22%3A51%2C%22height%22%3A28%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%22%2C%22x%22%3A93%2C%22y%22%3A1368%2C%22width%22%3A51%2C%22height%22%3A25%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fcfcfc%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u13068cf1%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"P3tun\" id=\"P3tun\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub218fd90\" id=\"ub218fd90\" style=\"color: rgb(25, 27, 31)\">存储型 XSS (Stored XSS)</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"ud4edddbd\" id=\"ud4edddbd\"><span data-lake-id=\"uff26f5ca\" id=\"uff26f5ca\" style=\"color: rgb(25, 27, 31)\">基于存储的 XSS 攻击，是通过提交带有恶意脚本的内容存储在服务器上，当其他人看到这些内容时发起 Web 攻击。一般提交的内容都是通过一些富文本编辑器编辑的，很容易插入危险代码。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u5af0f2f8\" id=\"u5af0f2f8\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F200222%2F1709618529333-ba83915f-62d4-45dc-a137-3a5be770ad68.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u9a971ee6-5f09-4c6c-8a87-46fc5ed5305%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u028d0fbe-9704-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A720%2C%22height%22%3A391%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A260675%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1440%2C%22originHeight%22%3A781%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22.%E5%AE%A2%E6%88%B7%E7%AB%AF%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E5%8F%8A%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%2C%E5%B9%B6%E5%B0%86%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96%E5%88%B0%E7%9A%84%22%2C%22x%22%3A757%2C%22y%22%3A126%2C%22width%22%3A410%2C%22height%22%3A30%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%95%8F%E6%84%9F%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E5%8F%91%E9%80%81%E7%BB%99%E6%94%BB%E5%87%BB%E8%80%85%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%22%2C%22x%22%3A789%2C%22y%22%3A163%2C%22width%22%3A342%2C%22height%22%3A28%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%94%BB%E5%87%BB%E8%80%85%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E7%9A%84%E6%95%8F%E6%84%9F%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%22%2C%22x%22%3A500%2C%22y%22%3A11%2C%22width%22%3A309%2C%22height%22%3A31%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%223.%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E8%A2%AB%E6%B3%A8%E5%85%A5%E7%9A%84%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%22%2C%22x%22%3A232%2C%22y%22%3A634%2C%22width%22%3A320%2C%22height%22%3A32%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E7%9F%A5%E5%B9%B3%40IRG%22%2C%22x%22%3A1048%2C%22y%22%3A694%2C%22width%22%3A274%2C%22height%22%3A44%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%94%BB%E5%87%BB%E8%80%85%E5%90%91WEB%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%22%2C%22x%22%3A13%2C%22y%22%3A319%2C%22width%22%3A268%2C%22height%22%3A27%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%94%BB%E5%87%BB%E8%80%85%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%22%2C%22x%22%3A1273%2C%22y%22%3A195%2C%22width%22%3A159%2C%22height%22%3A29%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%AD%98%E5%82%A8%22%2C%22x%22%3A993%2C%22y%22%3A671%2C%22width%22%3A128%2C%22height%22%3A34%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22WEB%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%22%2C%22x%22%3A648%2C%22y%22%3A721%2C%22width%22%3A152%2C%22height%22%3A30%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%E8%A2%AB%E6%B3%A8%E5%85%A5%E6%81%B6%E6%84%8F%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E9%A1%B5%22%2C%22x%22%3A277%2C%22y%22%3A687%2C%22width%22%3A278%2C%22height%22%3A28%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%8F%92%E5%85%A5%E6%81%B6%E6%84%8F%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%22%2C%22x%22%3A54%2C%22y%22%3A355%2C%22width%22%3A187%2C%22height%22%3A28%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E4%B8%89%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93%22%2C%22x%22%3A1270%2C%22y%22%3A722%2C%22width%22%3A127%2C%22height%22%3A31%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%94%BB%E5%87%BB%E8%80%85%22%2C%22x%22%3A38%2C%22y%22%3A219%2C%22width%22%3A78%2C%22height%22%3A27%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%22%2C%22x%22%3A42%2C%22y%22%3A726%2C%22width%22%3A58%2C%22height%22%3A30%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22GCFTAR%22%2C%22x%22%3A1286%2C%22y%22%3A700%2C%22width%22%3A110%2C%22height%22%3A30%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fbfbfb%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u1fe1913f%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"ud641c54e\" id=\"ud641c54e\"><span data-lake-id=\"u49d95b40\" id=\"u49d95b40\">​</span><br></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"I3R2K\" id=\"I3R2K\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf0afb2fb\" id=\"uf0afb2fb\">防范XSS（</span><span data-lake-id=\"uec21af05\" id=\"uec21af05\" style=\"color: rgb(25, 27, 31)\">Cross-site scripting </span><span data-lake-id=\"u3243a71e\" id=\"u3243a71e\">跨站脚本攻击）</span></h3><h4 data-lake-id=\"cBY6Q\" id=\"cBY6Q\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4f8689ee\" id=\"u4f8689ee\">攻击的方法包括：</span></h4><ol list=\"ud99f6f3c\"><li fid=\"u1878816c\" data-lake-id=\"u521a7969\" id=\"u521a7969\"><span data-lake-id=\"u36cc8491\" id=\"u36cc8491\">输入验证和过滤<br /></span><span data-lake-id=\"u626f68e9\" id=\"u626f68e9\">对用户输入进行验证：确保用户输入符合预期格式和范围，如邮箱、URL等。<br /></span><span data-lake-id=\"uc4980c05\" id=\"uc4980c05\">过滤特殊字符：对用户输入的特殊字符进行转义或过滤，如&lt;、&gt;、&amp;等。</span></li><li fid=\"u1878816c\" data-lake-id=\"ua8b1590b\" id=\"ua8b1590b\"><span data-lake-id=\"ucd9006ea\" id=\"ucd9006ea\">使用安全框架和库<br /></span><span data-lake-id=\"u648e8864\" id=\"u648e8864\">使用现成的安全框架和库：如Content Security Policy（CSP）、DOMPurify等，可以帮助防止XSS攻击。</span></li><li fid=\"u1878816c\" data-lake-id=\"uca7b57ae\" id=\"uca7b57ae\"><span data-lake-id=\"u09ab4ccb\" id=\"u09ab4ccb\">避免直接操作DOM<br /></span><span data-lake-id=\"u7d09cdc3\" id=\"u7d09cdc3\">避免直接操作DOM：使用框架提供的数据绑定和模板渲染功能，避免直接操作DOM。</span></li><li fid=\"u1878816c\" data-lake-id=\"u83c8227d\" id=\"u83c8227d\"><span data-lake-id=\"ua26ffd99\" id=\"ua26ffd99\">设置HttpOnly和Secure标记<br /></span><span data-lake-id=\"ub9b231b0\" id=\"ub9b231b0\">设置HttpOnly标记：确保cookie只能通过HTTP协议传输，防止被JavaScript访问。<br /></span><span data-lake-id=\"uc27ff029\" id=\"uc27ff029\">设置Secure标记：只在HTTPS连接中传输cookie，防止在非加密连接中泄露cookie信息。</span></li><li fid=\"u1878816c\" data-lake-id=\"u83a89ea3\" id=\"u83a89ea3\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2cd4702e\" id=\"u2cd4702e\">隔离用户输入和输出<br />对用户输入和输出进行隔离：不要直接将用户输入的内容插入到HTML、CSS或JavaScript代码中，使用innerText或textContent而不是innerHTML。</span><span data-lake-id=\"ucb3212f8\" id=\"ucb3212f8\">定期更新和维护<br /></span><span data-lake-id=\"u07b75043\" id=\"u07b75043\">定期更新框架和库：确保使用的框架和库是最新版本，以获取最新的安全补丁。<br /></span><span data-lake-id=\"u6f5e45e2\" id=\"u6f5e45e2\">监控和修复漏洞：定期进行安全审计，及时修复潜在的漏洞。</span></li><li fid=\"u1878816c\" data-lake-id=\"u445ea588\" id=\"u445ea588\"><span data-lake-id=\"u73824f83\" id=\"u73824f83\">教育和培训<br />对开发人员进行安全意识培训：教育开发人员关于XSS攻击的风险和防范措施，提高安全意识。<br />通过以上方法综合应用，可以有效防范XSS攻击，保护Web应用的安全性。</span></li></ol><p data-lake-id=\"ud8a5465f\" id=\"ud8a5465f\"><span data-lake-id=\"u7821186f\" id=\"u7821186f\">​</span><br></p>","body_draft":"<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"classic\"><p id=\"ud965b14c\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">XSS（</span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(25, 27, 31)\">Cross-site scripting </span><span class=\"ne-text\">跨站脚本攻击）</span></p><h3 id=\"d6QSM\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(25, 27, 31)\">反射型 XSS (Reflected XSS)</span></h3><p id=\"u07a2369e\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(25, 27, 31)\">反射型的 XSS 攻击，主要是由于服务端接收到客户端的不安全输入，在客户端触发执行从而发起 Web 攻击。</span></p><p id=\"u2c33f846\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/200222/1709618492845-cd1cd76a-fba0-428d-bd3a-a457a49747d4.png\" width=\"720\" id=\"u13068cf1\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><h3 id=\"P3tun\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(25, 27, 31)\">存储型 XSS (Stored XSS)</span></h3><p id=\"ud4edddbd\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(25, 27, 31)\">基于存储的 XSS 攻击，是通过提交带有恶意脚本的内容存储在服务器上，当其他人看到这些内容时发起 Web 攻击。一般提交的内容都是通过一些富文本编辑器编辑的，很容易插入危险代码。</span></p><p id=\"u5af0f2f8\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/200222/1709618529333-ba83915f-62d4-45dc-a137-3a5be770ad68.png\" width=\"720\" id=\"u1fe1913f\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"ud641c54e\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><h3 id=\"I3R2K\"><span class=\"ne-text\">防范XSS（</span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(25, 27, 31)\">Cross-site scripting </span><span class=\"ne-text\">跨站脚本攻击）</span></h3><h4 id=\"cBY6Q\"><span class=\"ne-text\">攻击的方法包括：</span></h4><ol class=\"ne-ol\"><li id=\"u521a7969\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">输入验证和过滤<br /></span><span class=\"ne-text\">对用户输入进行验证：确保用户输入符合预期格式和范围，如邮箱、URL等。<br /></span><span class=\"ne-text\">过滤特殊字符：对用户输入的特殊字符进行转义或过滤，如&lt;、&gt;、&amp;等。</span></li><li id=\"ua8b1590b\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">使用安全框架和库<br /></span><span class=\"ne-text\">使用现成的安全框架和库：如Content Security Policy（CSP）、DOMPurify等，可以帮助防止XSS攻击。</span></li><li id=\"uca7b57ae\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">避免直接操作DOM<br /></span><span class=\"ne-text\">避免直接操作DOM：使用框架提供的数据绑定和模板渲染功能，避免直接操作DOM。</span></li><li id=\"u83c8227d\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">设置HttpOnly和Secure标记<br /></span><span class=\"ne-text\">设置HttpOnly标记：确保cookie只能通过HTTP协议传输，防止被JavaScript访问。<br /></span><span class=\"ne-text\">设置Secure标记：只在HTTPS连接中传输cookie，防止在非加密连接中泄露cookie信息。</span></li><li id=\"u83a89ea3\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">隔离用户输入和输出<br />对用户输入和输出进行隔离：不要直接将用户输入的内容插入到HTML、CSS或JavaScript代码中，使用innerText或textContent而不是innerHTML。</span><span class=\"ne-text\">定期更新和维护<br /></span><span class=\"ne-text\">定期更新框架和库：确保使用的框架和库是最新版本，以获取最新的安全补丁。<br /></span><span class=\"ne-text\">监控和修复漏洞：定期进行安全审计，及时修复潜在的漏洞。</span></li><li id=\"u445ea588\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">教育和培训<br />对开发人员进行安全意识培训：教育开发人员关于XSS攻击的风险和防范措施，提高安全意识。<br />通过以上方法综合应用，可以有效防范XSS攻击，保护Web应用的安全性。</span></li></ol><p id=\"ud8a5465f\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p></div>","body_draft_asl":"<!doctype lake><meta name=\"doc-version\" content=\"1\" /><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"fixed\" /><meta name=\"typography\" content=\"classic\" /><meta name=\"paragraphSpacing\" content=\"relax\" /><p data-lake-id=\"ud965b14c\" id=\"ud965b14c\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6a7165e5\" id=\"u6a7165e5\">XSS（</span><span data-lake-id=\"u7ee4be53\" id=\"u7ee4be53\" style=\"color: rgb(25, 27, 31)\">Cross-site scripting </span><span data-lake-id=\"u35c1e225\" id=\"u35c1e225\">跨站脚本攻击）</span></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"d6QSM\" id=\"d6QSM\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6d8a2a5f\" id=\"u6d8a2a5f\" style=\"color: rgb(25, 27, 31)\">反射型 XSS (Reflected XSS)</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u07a2369e\" id=\"u07a2369e\"><span data-lake-id=\"u38e668f9\" id=\"u38e668f9\" style=\"color: rgb(25, 27, 31)\">反射型的 XSS 攻击，主要是由于服务端接收到客户端的不安全输入，在客户端触发执行从而发起 Web 攻击。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u2c33f846\" id=\"u2c33f846\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F200222%2F1709618492845-cd1cd76a-fba0-428d-bd3a-a457a49747d4.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u51035809-ab92-408a-912e-05896f765ef%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u028d0fbe-9704-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A720%2C%22height%22%3A708%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A320940%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1440%2C%22originHeight%22%3A1416%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%223.WEB%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%E6%B3%A8%E5%85%A5XSS%E7%9A%84%E7%BD%91%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E7%BB%99%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%22%2C%22x%22%3A451%2C%22y%22%3A575%2C%22width%22%3A505%2C%22height%22%3A26%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%88%96%E8%80%85%E4%BB%A5%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9B%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%22%2C%22x%22%3A1055%2C%22y%22%3A1108%2C%22width%22%3A328%2C%22height%22%3A25%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%8F%91%E9%80%81%E6%81%B6%E6%84%8F%E9%93%BE%E6%8E%A5%E7%BB%99%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%