A2%AB%E6%B3%A8%E5%85%A5%E6%81%B6%E6%84%8F%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E9%A1%B5%22%2C%22x%22%3A277%2C%22y%22%3A687%2C%22width%22%3A278%2C%22height%22%3A28%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%8F%92%E5%85%A5%E6%81%B6%E6%84%8F%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%22%2C%22x%22%3A54%2C%22y%22%3A355%2C%22width%22%3A187%2C%22height%22%3A28%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E4%B8%89%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93%22%2C%22x%22%3A1270%2C%22y%22%3A722%2C%22width%22%3A127%2C%22height%22%3A31%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%94%BB%E5%87%BB%E8%80%85%22%2C%22x%22%3A38%2C%22y%22%3A219%2C%22width%22%3A78%2C%22height%22%3A27%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%22%2C%22x%22%3A42%2C%22y%22%3A726%2C%22width%22%3A58%2C%22height%22%3A30%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22GCFTAR%22%2C%22x%22%3A1286%2C%22y%22%3A700%2C%22width%22%3A110%2C%22height%22%3A30%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fbfbfb%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u1fe1913f%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"ud641c54e\" id=\"ud641c54e\"><span data-lake-id=\"u49d95b40\" id=\"u49d95b40\">​</span><br></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"I3R2K\" id=\"I3R2K\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf0afb2fb\" id=\"uf0afb2fb\">防范XSS（</span><span data-lake-id=\"uec21af05\" id=\"uec21af05\" style=\"color: rgb(25, 27, 31)\">Cross-site scripting </span><span data-lake-id=\"u3243a71e\" id=\"u3243a71e\">跨站脚本攻击）</span></h3><h4 data-lake-id=\"cBY6Q\" id=\"cBY6Q\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4f8689ee\" id=\"u4f8689ee\">攻击的方法包括：</span></h4><ol list=\"ud99f6f3c\"><li fid=\"u1878816c\" data-lake-id=\"u521a7969\" id=\"u521a7969\"><span data-lake-id=\"u36cc8491\" id=\"u36cc8491\">输入验证和过滤<br /></span><span data-lake-id=\"u626f68e9\" id=\"u626f68e9\">对用户输入进行验证：确保用户输入符合预期格式和范围，如邮箱、URL等。<br /></span><span data-lake-id=\"uc4980c05\" id=\"uc4980c05\">过滤特殊字符：对用户输入的特殊字符进行转义或过滤，如&lt;、&gt;、&amp;等。</span></li><li fid=\"u1878816c\" data-lake-id=\"ua8b1590b\" id=\"ua8b1590b\"><span data-lake-id=\"ucd9006ea\" id=\"ucd9006ea\">使用安全框架和库<br /></span><span data-lake-id=\"u648e8864\" id=\"u648e8864\">使用现成的安全框架和库：如Content Security Policy（CSP）、DOMPurify等，可以帮助防止XSS攻击。</span></li><li fid=\"u1878816c\" data-lake-id=\"uca7b57ae\" id=\"uca7b57ae\"><span data-lake-id=\"u09ab4ccb\" id=\"u09ab4ccb\">避免直接操作DOM<br /></span><span data-lake-id=\"u7d09cdc3\" id=\"u7d09cdc3\">避免直接操作DOM：使用框架提供的数据绑定和模板渲染功能，避免直接操作DOM。</span></li><li fid=\"u1878816c\" data-lake-id=\"u83c8227d\" id=\"u83c8227d\"><span data-lake-id=\"ua26ffd99\" id=\"ua26ffd99\">设置HttpOnly和Secure标记<br /></span><span data-lake-id=\"ub9b231b0\" id=\"ub9b231b0\">设置HttpOnly标记：确保cookie只能通过HTTP协议传输，防止被JavaScript访问。<br /></span><span data-lake-id=\"uc27ff029\" id=\"uc27ff029\">设置Secure标记：只在HTTPS连接中传输cookie，防止在非加密连接中泄露cookie信息。</span></li><li fid=\"u1878816c\" data-lake-id=\"u83a89ea3\" id=\"u83a89ea3\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2cd4702e\" id=\"u2cd4702e\">隔离用户输入和输出<br />对用户输入和输出进行隔离：不要直接将用户输入的内容插入到HTML、CSS或JavaScript代码中，使用innerText或textContent而不是innerHTML。</span><span data-lake-id=\"ucb3212f8\" id=\"ucb3212f8\">定期更新和维护<br /></span><span data-lake-id=\"u07b75043\" id=\"u07b75043\">定期更新框架和库：确保使用的框架和库是最新版本，以获取最新的安全补丁。<br /></span><span data-lake-id=\"u6f5e45e2\" id=\"u6f5e45e2\">监控和修复漏洞：定期进行安全审计，及时修复潜在的漏洞。</span></li><li fid=\"u1878816c\" data-lake-id=\"u445ea588\" id=\"u445ea588\"><span data-lake-id=\"u73824f83\" id=\"u73824f83\">教育和培训<br />对开发人员进行安全意识培训：教育开发人员关于XSS攻击的风险和防范措施，提高安全意识。<br />通过以上方法综合应用，可以有效防范XSS攻击，保护Web应用的安全性。</span></li></ol><p data-lake-id=\"ud8a5465f\" id=\"ud8a5465f\"><span data-lake-id=\"u7821186f\" id=\"u7821186f\">​</span><br></p>","word_count":592,"slug":"adefqrozip81mwyr","type":"Doc","title":"如何防范XSS攻击","public":1,"cover":"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/200222/1709618492845-cd1cd76a-fba0-428d-bd3a-a457a49747d4.png","custom_cover":"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/200222/1709618492845-cd1cd76a-fba0-428d-bd3a-a457a49747d4.png","description":"XSS（Cross-site scripting 跨站脚本攻击）反射型 XSS (Reflected XSS)反射型的 XSS 攻击，主要是由于服务端接收到客户端的不安全输入，在客户端触发执行从而发起 Web 攻击。存储型 XSS (Stored XSS)基于存储的 XSS 攻击，是通过提交带...","custom_description":"","format":"lake","status":1,"read_status":1,"editor_meta":"{\"image\":2}","user_id":200222,"created_at":"2024-03-05T05:55:57.000Z","updated_at":"2026-03-06T08:24:07.000Z","published_at":"2024-03-05T06:05:15.000Z","first_published_at":"2024-03-05T05:56:15.640Z","content_updated_at":"2024-03-05T06:05:15.000Z","id":160628207},"doc_digest":"Oqc4dsyDETxkJQQ4ADNPrm-SEso"}